# Bottom Navigation & Tabs

## Order & Implementation
- **Tab Order**: Profile → Discover → Properties → Liked → Visits
- **Primary widget**: [lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart)
- **Center tab**: Routes to main swipe interface (Home/Properties module)

## Routes & Consistency
- Each tab maps to named route in `app_routes.dart` and page in `app_pages.dart`
- Tabs available across all primary screens
- No ad-hoc navigation bars per view

## Accessibility
- Labels must be localized (`.tr`)
- Meet contrast and tap target guidelines